blog.name: lrsoarp
blog.title: London Royal School Of Arts
blog.description: London Royal School of Arts is the most prestigious school in the world. Its initial focus was to provide for high class society students but the school has since grown to be able to accommodate all social economic classes. the admittance stakes are high and most of the students will have to go through auditions before they can begin their journey. Few are here by invitation and it’s their exceptional talent that has earned them this ticket. There’s no doubt that at the end of this long path, the students of LRSOA will become successful in their everyday lives. But under all the big titles and stressing expectations of parents and teachers, there is friendship, love, drama, rivalry and parties that thrive in this large campus. So what about you? Are you ready to begin?
